Text: New Opportunityall I just wanted to let all of you know that my last day at Enron is October I have decided to take a position with Deloitte and Touche Its an excellent opportunity and Im looking forward to getting started I hope all of you will keep in touch My home number is and my home email address is Feel free to call any time Ill be in touch once I get settled in at Deloitte and Touche Have a great weekend Alysia
